features.text:
# How Swag0x Works
It's a Web3 onboarding exercise with  tangible  rewards. You can go from knowing near nothing about cryptocurrencies to transacting on the public Ethereum blockchain in just a few step by using our tokens to acquire NFTs (non-fungible tokens) then completing a swag transaction paid for with these tokens. In one click we give you a new Web3 address/account, a free X5T token and team badge. 
There are no strings attached.  
This is Web3; no usernames and no passwords. 
No centralized service housing your data. The NFTs are yours to keep and permanently held in the public blockchain. The swag is shipped to you almost anywhere in the world.

# About the Badges
The badges were designed as a team-building project using Web3 technology. The team badges allow users to associate with a NFT badge so that group mebers can operate under a unique banner.  The Skill Level Badges can be used for any purpose, however, we have designed a way to make it fun and educational at the same time.  

Go ahead and select a team team badge and you can get started using the Web3 ecosystem without providing any private or personal information.  Then select a skill badge line you would like to start using.  Each level will provide you a permanent NFT and perks to use in the Swag0x store and the larger 
Web3vm ecosystem.

# Select your preferred skill

You will receive a NFT badge for each level you complete.

Each badge has six (6) levels.

| Level      | Cost     |
| ----------- |:---------:|
| 1. Common  | 10 X5T |
| 2. Starter       | 100 X5T
| 3. Getting There | 200 X5T
| 4. Arrived       | 500 X5T
| 5. Made It       | 1000 X5T
| 6. Master        | 2000 X5T


This training is primarily about navigating Web3 technology not accreditation. Each skill level can either be purchased or earned through tasks and reading knowledge base.
